Description: Arabia Insurance Cooperative (known as: AICC) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since February 2008. AICC operates within the Insurance sector focusing on Multi-line Insurance. It has company operating across Saudi Arabia, working on Property and Casualty Insurance. AICC is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in December 2007.
